      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity is considered medium due to the involvement of multiple tables, conditional logic, and the use of a subquery to determine which records to delete. The procedure also involves handling optional parameters and outputting results, which adds to its complexity."
        }
