                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Concurrency",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": If the procedure is executed concurrently by multiple sessions, it could lead to locking issues, especially if a large number of rows are being deleted."
